text.headline: Cadre
text.text: A real estate technology startup co-founded and partly owned by White House senior adviser Jared Kushner. Kushner doesn't play an active role in Cadre's operations, company officials say when asked about the president's son-in-law. But he hasn't divested his Cadre stake
